        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Caspia makarovi: (A) apertural view of the adult shell; (B, C) apical and lateral views of the protoconch of the same specimen as in A; (D, E) detailed apical views of the same embryonic shell; (F) Caspia sp,: initial part of embryonic shell of recently hatched juvenile specimen of Caspia sp., apart from fine reticulate ornamentation the presence of fine spiral thread along the suture can be seen." ;
