<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4607502>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 6. Radulae of some Caspiinae and Hydrobiinae: (A) rachidian tooth of Caspia gmelinii Clessin and W. Dybowski in W. Dybowski, 1887 (redrawn after Sitnikova and Satrobogatov 1998: 1361, fig. 3, 12); (B) Caspiohydrobia sidorovi Starobogatov and Andreeva, 1981; (C) Caspiohydrobia behningi Starobogatov and Andreeva, 1981; (D) rachidian tooth of Caspiohydrobia convexa Logvinenko and Starobogatov in Golikov and Starobogatov 1966 (redrawn after Sitnikova et al. 1992: 5, fig. 1, 17, 18, 21). Abbreviations: rach, rachidian (central) tooth; lat, lateral tooth; marg, marginal teeth." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4607502/files/figure.png" .

