<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4607492>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Caspia knipowitchii: (A) apertural view of the adult shell; (B, C) apical and lateral views of the protoconch of the same specimen as in A; (D) apertural view of the juvenile shell; (E, F) detailed lateral views of the embryonic shell of the same specimen as in D; (G) apical view of the protoconch of the same specimen as in D; (H, I) close-up of the same embryonic shell as in D: specific fine reticulate sculpture on the surface of the embryonic shell are seen, WE, width of initial cap-like part of embryonic shell." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4607492/files/figure.png" .

